My meme

My meme is a “reaction” style meme which is meant to to be sent as a reaction to something.

library(magick)

# Details of the text box
text_box <- image_blank(width = 400,
            height = 100,
            color = "#DEDEDE") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "My honest reaction:",
                 color = "#000000",
                 size = 40,
                 font = "Impact",
                 gravity = "center")

ryan_gosling <- image_read("https://media.gq.com/photos/63371e057eeeca09549d75e8/1:1/w_1683,h_1683,c_limit/GU774_LUGGAGE%20RG_DPS_PR%20CROPS_150dpi_5.jpeg")%>%
  image_scale(400)

meme_vector <- c(text_box, ryan_gosling)

final_meme <- image_append(meme_vector, stack = TRUE)
final_meme

image_write(final_meme, "my_meme.png")

My animated GIF

My animated GIF shows famous pop culture characters that Gen Z relates to

library(magick)


#Creation of text box
text_box <- image_blank(width = 600,
                        height = 100,
                        color = "#DEDEDE") %>%
  image_annotate(text = "Wow, he's literally me",
                 color = "#000000",
                 size = 40,
                 font = "Impact",
                 gravity = "center")

doomer_guy <- image_read("https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/035/981/EPlwBwIXsAAwfCH.jpg")%>%
  image_scale(300)


#Creation of first frame of animation
patrick <- image_read("https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/52/American-psycho-patrick-bateman.jpg")%>%
  image_scale(300)
frame1_vector <- c(doomer_guy, patrick)
frame1_bottom_half <- image_append(frame1_vector)
frame1_final_vector <- c(text_box, frame1_bottom_half)
frame1 <- image_append(frame1_final_vector, stack = TRUE)


#Creation of second frame of animation
batman <- image_read("https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/2022_thebatman_alamy_2000x1270-696x442.jpg")%>%
  image_scale(300)
frame2_vector <- c(doomer_guy, batman)
frame2_bottom_half <- image_append(frame2_vector)
frame2_final_vector <- c(text_box, frame2_bottom_half)
frame2 <- image_append(frame2_final_vector, stack = TRUE)


#Creation of third frame of animation
kd <- image_read("https://www.slashfilm.com/img/gallery/blade-runner-2049-ending-explained-a-fresh-twist-on-the-old-chosen-one-narrative/l-intro-1634571326.jpg")%>%
  image_scale(300)
frame3_vector <- c(doomer_guy, kd)
frame3_bottom_half <- image_append(frame3_vector)
frame3_final_vector <- c(text_box, frame3_bottom_half)
frame3 <- image_append(frame3_final_vector, stack = TRUE)


#Creation of fourth frame of animation
homelander <- image_read("https://www.hollywoodinsider.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Hollywood-Insider-The-Boys-Homelander.png")%>%
  image_scale(300)
frame4_vector <- c(doomer_guy, homelander)
frame4_bottom_half <- image_append(frame4_vector)
frame4_final_vector <- c(text_box, frame4_bottom_half)
frame4 <- image_append(frame4_final_vector, stack = TRUE)


# Animating the meme

frames <- c(frame1, frame2, frame3, frame4)

animated_meme <- image_animate(frames, fps = 1)

image_write(animated_meme, "my_animation.gif")
